name: Catify
body:
### Welcome Catify, hosted by Github Pages!

Here's an example of how to get a cat to walk around on your webpage. I loved the game Alleycat as a kit, so here it is, a crappy imitation. I need to finish the rest of the animation frames but the basic walking and blinking is working.

To try it out, use the arrow keys!
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
